description:
CUUP5qiTable:  A table containing Ericsson-specific CUUP 5QI configuration data for specific cells, identified by time, area, and cell ID.

dateTime: Timestamp of the configuration record.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (appears to be identical to CellId).
Id3: An identifier with an unknown meaning (only value '1' observed).
vsDataType: Type of data, specifying it as a CUUP5qiTable.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format, indicating Ericsson-specific attributes.
CUUP5qiTable.default5qiTable: Boolean indicating if this is a default 5QI configuration.
CUUP5qiTable.reservedBy:  Field indicating who reserved this configuration (currently empty).
CUUP5qiTable.cUUP5qiTableId: Unique ID for this specific CUUP 5QI table entry.
